eegdev (0.0-0alpha8) lucid; urgency=low

  * Add gtec hack: 200ms delay between slave and master acquisition start.
  * Switch to 3.0 (quilt) format.
  * Remove unncessary build-dependency on libc6-dev (build-essential).
  * Bump Standards-version to 3.9.2
  * Tighten build-dependency on debhelper to >= 7.0.50~, due to _override
    rules.
  * Only provide an unversioned libxdffileio-dev package but still provides
    libeegdev0-dev as virtual package.

 -- Nicolas Bourdaud <nicolas.bourdaud@gmail.com>  Tue, 25 Oct 2011 17:34:49 +0200

