eegdev (0.0-0alpha2) lucid; urgency=low

  * Separate packages into 2 flavors: free and gtec (not addon any longer)
  * Add symbols file to binary packages
  * Fix udev rules
  * Handle interrupted child or parent
  * Make procdev init fails gracefully
  * Multiple race condition fixes in procdev
  * One minor race condition in egd_start

